{"tid":388531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子疑過激性行為離奇死亡　警重案接手查","createTime":"2017-09-05T13:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T03:01:11.000Z","uid":26769,"like":90,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec44a10fe67da89fb2d3d352646f7dc2d988399c","tid":388531,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"女子衣衫不整身有血離奇死亡　警重案接手查<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170905/bkn-20170905205543193-0905_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170905%2Fbkn-20170905205543193-0905_00822_001.html&d=03AktAJquTfWmOz0pf1dJi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f5368698\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170905/bkn-20170905205543193-0905_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山女子離奇死亡。晚上近7時，一名男子返回錦豐苑錦萱閣住所時，赫見胞姊倒臥家中，口吐白沫陷於昏迷，由於其身上有血、衣衫不整，懷疑她曾受性侵，慌忙報警求助。救護員趕至現場，將女事主抬上擔架床，由救護車將她送院，證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，女事主有身體病紀錄，經醫生初步檢查後，不排除她事發前曾與人發生過激性行為，未知是否與死因直接關係。由於事件撲朔迷離，沙田警區重案組接手調查，暫時未確定事件是否有可疑。現已聯絡到女事主一名男友人助查，正調查他是否與案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姦到死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d063e7c5d38a88e5f6a0d9f1ee6483417526c5","tid":388531,"uid":19676,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:51:53.000Z","msg":"屌死左"},{"pid":"3ba98f24f6217a25d32615061cd0a2bae4584055","tid":388531,"uid":6192,"like":325,"dislike":2,"score":323,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"呢幾日d新聞好得人驚"},{"pid":"fc813a58e2d185d30261c49070336cf97bbf384e","tid":388531,"uid":828,"like":164,"dislike":339,"score":-175,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"從前有個人叫阿爽。<br />\n<br />\n他死掉了。 。 。<br />\n<br />\n出殯那天。<br />\n<br />\n他的家人哭喊：爽阿&hellip;&hellip;爽阿。<br />\n<br />\n路人不解。問道：&lsquo;你們爽什麼啊。 &rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n家人痛哭流涕：爽死了&hellip;&hellip;爽死了!!"},{"pid":"f2f3b2ad33cadd03679e5ce55b0f2ea94f702e8b","tid":388531,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"769993689c12ae2752faa9eedbd8e2dcb159a318","tid":388531,"uid":138860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:53:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8a2f499b9167afdd11a93fe81a0ff53fbaae1f6","tid":388531,"uid":7840,"like":40,"dislike":203,"score":-163,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0886dcd13597122ad1bf7cb1403830a8e15777d8","tid":388531,"uid":62167,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"真係屌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735a9c2b3fcf871fa020131adc3e0ac17042d2f9","tid":388531,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打出黎認左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a4dff084c7e9f16cfbbcb7bae6060bcceb90e9","tid":388531,"uid":29625,"like":148,"dislike":1,"score":147,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫身體病紀錄 百份啲記者唔好再垃圾啲"},{"pid":"5058a294ceb9a27ee9abba4f8722d2c1a95cce68","tid":388531,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:02:45.000Z","msg":"真係屌撚死你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44e321949b91d78d50ce4b46c8dd5c5fd86a7b2","tid":388531,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4915ce6a95f9cb6b3436d830f45d79c3810db21","tid":388531,"uid":1582,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"cit