迷，由於其身上有血、衣衫不整，懷疑她曾受性侵，慌忙報警求助。救護員趕至現場，將女事主抬上擔架床，由救護車將她送院，證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，女事主有身體病紀錄，經醫生初步檢查後，不排除她事發前曾與人發生過激性行為，未知是否與死因直接關係。由於事件撲朔迷離，沙田警區重案組接手調查，暫時未確定事件是否有可疑。現已聯絡到女事主一名男友人助查，正調查他是否與案件有關。</blockquote><br />\n鮑姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2720f8ad5ffa0a45224f11464a9511935370f0f","tid":388531,"uid":136355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:51:37.000Z","msg":"呢排咁多人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7月14<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793115c4119ab80fb23c343212f8569b44c58b0b","tid":388531,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"根據劇情係搵到個男人，跟住個男人用lan線自殺 🤔"},{"pid":"c8675477c302de554e23591986e9d07daacb8ccc","tid":388531,"uid":110589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"病發致死會下身赤裸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa61cfbfe3e899513c33e7c9f1f63b15bf2b98b","tid":388531,"uid":117628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:18:02.000Z","msg":"報紙佬咪亂寫啦，紅斑狼瘡症既「傷口」多數係塊面而唔係身，亦唔會流血，而類風濕關節炎更加唔會有傷口，兩個病都係長期病，冇所謂「病發」"},{"pid":"97e81f3585e55092bad7bb8c0e91ea67dc38e497","tid":388531,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:18:11.000Z","msg":"我就屌撚死你！！！"},{"pid":"29c515661056b63a925fcb3f5f250afc0cb60c50","tid":388531,"uid":62809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅斑狼瘡病發可以咁撚樣?<br />\n報紙佬想呃邊個</blockquote><br />\n紅斑狼瘡發病 可以好厲害 全身器官可以發炎 出血 衰竭而死 依個病非常恐怖"},{"pid":"f66afdbb945c7a079cd4ac39d45cc5de6f00e145","tid":388531,"uid":4190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZBFZr-AU3I0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZBFZr-AU3I0&d=03AktAJquTfWmOz0pf1d